divs: Sighting DetailsTRAVELING SOUTHBOUND TURNPIKE AT AROUND HOLLYWOOD BLVD, BROWARD COUNTY, NOTICED RECTANGULAR OBJECT MOVING SE TOWARDS OCEAN. FIRST OBJECT PASSED. WHILE DRIVING AT 60 MILES PER HOUR USED IPHONE 5 TO SNAP TWO PICTURES BY AIMING IN DIRECTION OF OBJECTS. COULD NOT LOOK THROUGH SIGHT. JUST AIMED CAMERA AND HOPED FOR THE BEST. OBJECTS LOOKED RECTANGULAR WITH SQUARES VISIBLE LIKE THE MICROSOFT LOGO.
